🎥 Prime Video Dashboard🎥

  
🌟 Project Overview:
The Prime Video Dashboard is an interactive business intelligence solution built using Power BI. 
Designed to analyze key performance indicators (KPIs), this dashboard visualizes trends, tracks user behavior, and 
delivers actionable insights to enhance decision-making and optimize business operations for Prime Video.

🔑 Key Features:
  
📊 Comprehensive KPI Analysis:
Tracks vital metrics like total views, revenue, watch time, subscription growth, and churn rate.
Provides stakeholders with a clear, high-level overview of business performance.
  
🎨 Interactive Visualizations:
Includes dynamic charts, graphs, and slicers for intuitive data presentation.
Drill-through functionality for deeper analysis of data points.
  
📈 Trend and Behavior Analysis:
Examines trends in viewer engagement, popular genres, regional performance, and seasonal variations.
Unveils user preferences to refine content strategies.
  
⚙️ Optimized Data Models:
Cleanses and integrates data from multiple sources for accuracy and reliability.
Leverages advanced DAX calculations for precise insights.
  
🖥️ User-Friendly Design:
Intuitive layout with easy-to-use filters for quick navigation.
Accessible insights tailored for both technical and non-technical users.
  
🛠️ Tools and Technologies:
Data Visualization: Power BI
Data Cleaning & Preparation: Power Query
Data Modeling: DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
Data Sources: Aggregated data (e.g., subscriptions, viewership, revenue streams)
  
💡 Use Cases:
📺 Content Strategy Optimization:
Identify trending genres and high-engagement content to guide future production.

📊 Business Performance Monitoring:
Assess subscription growth, churn rates, and revenue trends for a complete performance review.

🌍 Regional Insights:
Analyze viewership by region to tailor marketing and content strategies.

