🚀 How to Use:
Clone this repository.
Open the .pbix file in Power BI Desktop.
Connect the dashboard to your data source (optional for real-time updates).
Explore interactive visuals and uncover valuable insights!
  
🌟 Project Highlights:
This project demonstrates expertise in data visualization, business intelligence, and decision-making. 
It exemplifies how raw data can be transformed into actionable insights, enabling businesses to thrive in a data-driven environment.

